{"tid":1312551,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[發夢]見到前面走 記得停低問點解","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:47:34.000Z","uid":85791,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d72becc6ed66784ee9eb0e2ccc8c78dcac17fec6","tid":1312551,"uid":85791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"人走你又走，一野走哂邊個保護前面既義士？<br />\n雖然有d人未準備好做勇武，但都要守住其他手足，一個都不能少。<br />\n係現場大家都好驚，但係請大家冷靜，問清楚前面咩情況，唔好人走你又走。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家記得停低，<br />\n問走嘅人發生咩事點解走，<br />\n用自己理智判斷，<br />\n唔好盲從！</span></span><br />\n聽日都係，遊行乜人都有，有d人真係未見過狗，可能一下子好驚。<br />\n發夢呢件事係金鐘到今日上水都有人唔明，大家一定要守住自己手足，要走一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfaa1fbfbb718d52bb3f1378a34312145274c64f","tid":1312551,"uid":85791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3344c5a0473339f772587a0f240182a20a58b586","tid":1312551,"uid":85791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8fcb59dcce025111d3aecba05421fa052b5db5","tid":1312551,"uid":18786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"如果大家可以一路走嗌發生咩會唔會仲好？<br />\n兵荒馬亂好難問咁多"},{"pid":"b55485bca402161bd5a2205cade3436875b3be28","tid":1312551,"uid":18786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果大家可以一路走一路嗌發生咩事會唔會仲好？<br />\n兵荒馬亂好難問咁多</blockquote>"},{"pid":"80b7dc45e8755f254b8d7ecee5855c27092572d1","tid":1312551,"uid":85791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b55485bca402161bd5a2205cade3436875b3be28","tid":1312551,"uid":18786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果大家可以一路走一路嗌發生咩事會唔會仲好？<br />\n兵荒馬亂好難問咁多</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"做到咁當然最好，但好多時前面既人叫退後，問返佢係唔知發生咩事"},{"pid":"3e6c924fc07437a2df768ffd5a553df38afaa00d","tid":1312551,"uid":85791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:19:59.000Z","msg":"推，前線後援應該留意"},{"pid":"2901f95e8d13d5efd2591dc876c1f9c8f72b074d","tid":1312551,"uid":85791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前面走既人要大叫點解走，<br />\n後面唔知點解走既人一定要問</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d2282979921afc9622d445d02e5edac0c17dba9","tid":1312551,"uid":85791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}